a:6:{i:0;a:32:{s:2:"id";s:2:"15";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:13:"post_keywords";s:0:"";s:6:"duties";s:6:"院长";s:3:"job";s:15:"副主任医师";s:12:"working_time";s:41:"11,21,31,41,51,61,71,13,23,33,43,53,63,73";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2000-01-01 00:00:00";s:7:"content";s:67:"<p>即刻用高难种植牙，各种口腔临床疑难病例。</p>";s:4:"name";s:9:"蔡明河";s:7:"term_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"excerpt";s:731:"<p>从事口腔临床工作20余年，既是口腔颌面外科的专家，也是种植牙名医。“即刻负重”种植牙技术传入中国时，蔡明河就是第一批接触新技术的医生。2015年，就带领种植团队开展“即刻负重”种植牙技术，有上万颗种植牙成功案例。</p><p>擅长高难种植，很多其他口腔机构都难以接诊的高难种植手术，经蔡明河仔细检查后，总会给出这样的答案：“可以克服，困难不大。”这正是因为其多年在口腔颌面外科的经验，口腔颌面外科涉及的范围更广，且面对的基本都是大型手术、极高难度手术，所以很多的高难种植牙对他来说，也仅仅是普通病例。</p>";s:11:"post_status";s:1:"1";s:14:"comment_status";s:1:"1";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-09-11 14:24:01";s:21:"post_content_filtered";N;s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";N;s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:5:"smeta";s:149:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20181226\/5c22e74110e76.png","thumb_phone":"\/data\/upload\/20180911\/5b9760089eaa7.png","template":"","template_phone":""}";s:9:"post_hits";s:3:"892";s:9:"post_like";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:11:"recommended";s:1:"1";s:10:"post_phone";N;s:9:"link_type";s:1:"1";s:8:"post_url";s:0:"";s:11:"post_extend";s:878:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20180911\/5b975fc84b794.png","thumb1":"\/data\/upload\/20181205\/5c07901aa99ae.jpg","post_extend1":"\u5373\u523b\u7528\u9ad8\u96be\u79cd\u690d\u7259\u3001\u5404\u79cd\u53e3\u8154\u4e34\u5e8a\u7591\u96be\u75c5\u4f8b","post_extend2":"\u79cd\u690d\u4e13\u5bb6\u53f7","post_extend3":"10","post_extend4":"\u6210\u90fd\u5fb7\u9053\u53e3\u8154\u533b\u9662\u9662\u957f","post_extend5":"\u6210\u90fd\u5fb7\u9053\u53e3\u8154\u533b\u9662\u9662\u957f,\u6cb3\u5357\u533b\u79d1\u5927\u5b66\u53e3\u8154\u533b\u5b66\u7855\u58eb,\u6cb3\u5357\u7701\u533b\u9662\u7ba1\u7406\u534f\u4f1a\u53e3\u8154\u5206\u4f1a\u5e38\u59d4,\u6cb3\u5357\u7701\u6297\u764c\u534f\u4f1a\u5934\u9888\u4e13\u4e1a\u59d4\u5458\u4f1a\u59d4\u5458,\u201c\u5373\u523b\u7528\u201d\u9ad8\u96be\u79cd\u690d\u7259\u9886\u57df\u9886\u519b\u4eba\u7269","post_extend6":"","post_extend7":"","post_extend8":""}";s:7:"isfixed";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_murl";s:0:"";s:10:"compatible";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"1";}i:1;a:32:{s:2:"id";s:2:"20";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:13:"post_keywords";s:0:"";s:6:"duties";s:15:"种植科主任";s:3:"job";s:12:"主治医师";s:12:"working_time";N;s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2000-01-01 00:00:00";s:7:"content";s:490:"<p>毕业于哈尔滨医科大学，专业从事口腔临床工作十余年，先后在北京、西安等地参与国际先进种植牙技术培训与进修，积累了丰富的口腔种植理论及实践经验，熟练掌握各项先进的口腔诊疗技术，不断精益求精，在微创无痛技术上面有较深的造诣。工作中坚持以高尚的医德医风、严谨的执业方式为患者提供更科学、全面的口腔修复方案，帮助实现良好的修复效果。</p>";s:4:"name";s:9:"李加亮";s:7:"term_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"excerpt";s:490:"<p>毕业于哈尔滨医科大学，专业从事口腔临床工作十余年，先后在北京、西安等地参与国际先进种植牙技术培训与进修，积累了丰富的口腔种植理论及实践经验，熟练掌握各项先进的口腔诊疗技术，不断精益求精，在微创无痛技术上面有较深的造诣。工作中坚持以高尚的医德医风、严谨的执业方式为患者提供更科学、全面的口腔修复方案，帮助实现良好的修复效果。</p>";s:11:"post_status";s:1:"1";s:14:"comment_status";s:1:"1";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2019-07-10 14:54:36";s:21:"post_content_filtered";N;s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";N;s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:5:"smeta";s:149:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258c609d985.jpg","thumb_phone":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258be52df4d.jpg","template":"","template_phone":""}";s:9:"post_hits";s:1:"7";s:9:"post_like";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:11:"recommended";s:1:"1";s:10:"post_phone";N;s:9:"link_type";s:1:"1";s:8:"post_url";s:0:"";s:11:"post_extend";s:644:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258df6ea3e6.jpg","thumb1":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258c044cba6.jpg","post_extend1":"\u5fae\u521b\u65e0\u75db\u79cd\u690d\u53ca\u4fee\u590d\u3001\u5fae\u521b\u65e0\u75db\u62d4\u7259\uff0c\u5404\u7c7b\u79cd\u690d\u540e\u7cbe\u51c6\u4fee\u590d\u3001\u7259\u5468\u75c5\u7684\u8bca\u65ad\u53ca\u57fa\u7840\u6cbb\u7597","post_extend2":"\u79cd\u690d\u4e13\u5bb6\u53f7","post_extend3":"","post_extend4":"\u6df1\u5733\u5fb7\u9053\u53e3\u8154\u79cd\u690d\u79d1\u4e3b\u4efb","post_extend5":"\u6df1\u5733\u5fb7\u9053\u53e3\u8154\u79cd\u690d\u79d1\u4e3b\u4efb","post_extend6":"","post_extend7":"","post_extend8":""}";s:7:"isfixed";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_murl";s:0:"";s:10:"compatible";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"2";}i:2;a:32:{s:2:"id";s:2:"10";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:13:"post_keywords";s:0:"";s:6:"duties";s:6:"主任";s:3:"job";s:12:"主任医师";s:12:"working_time";s:41:"11,21,31,41,51,61,71,13,23,33,43,53,63,73";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2000-01-01 00:00:00";s:7:"content";s:52:"<p>即刻用种植、微创种植、种植修复</p>";s:4:"name";s:9:"黄亦凡";s:7:"term_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"excerpt";s:631:"<p>黄主任1975年12月毕业于华西医科大学口腔系，是成都军区总医院口腔科主任，从事口腔临床工作四十余年，始终保持着学习的态度，为自己积累了丰富的口腔医学经验。退休后先后在四川大学华西口腔医院，华西牙种植医院工作。黄主任在口腔内科、外科、修复、口腔种植等专业的临床工作中有丰富的经验，具备处理各种口腔复杂疑难临床病例的操作技能。多次应邀参加学术交流，并在国内外口腔权威专业刊物上发表论文数十余篇，获得了业内人士的一致认同和赞赏。</p>";s:11:"post_status";s:1:"1";s:14:"comment_status";s:1:"1";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-06-20 17:20:17";s:21:"post_content_filtered";N;s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";N;s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:5:"smeta";s:149:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20180822\/5b7d1393e499d.jpg","thumb_phone":"\/data\/upload\/20180620\/5b2a2543c14a5.jpg","template":"","template_phone":""}";s:9:"post_hits";s:3:"728";s:9:"post_like";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:11:"recommended";s:1:"1";s:10:"post_phone";N;s:9:"link_type";s:1:"0";s:8:"post_url";s:0:"";s:11:"post_extend";s:738:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20180620\/5b2a254a92a47.jpg","thumb1":"\/data\/upload\/20190603\/5cf483336eab0.png","post_extend1":"\u5373\u523b\u7528\u79cd\u690d\u3001\u5fae\u521b\u79cd\u690d\u3001\u200b\u79cd\u690d\u4fee\u590d\u3001\u53e3\u8154\u5185\u79d1\u3001\u5916\u79d1","post_extend2":"","post_extend3":"","post_extend4":"","post_extend5":"\u5373\u523b\u7528\u79cd\u690d\u7259\u6280\u672f\u6307\u5bfc,\u79cd\u690d\u7259\u4fee\u590d\u6743\u5a01\u4e13\u5bb6,\u4e2d\u534e\u53e3\u8154\u533b\u5b66\u4f1a\u4f1a\u5458,\u4e2d\u534e\u53e3\u8154\u533b\u5b66\u4f1a\u6210\u90fd\u5206\u4f1a\u5e38\u59d4,\u66fe\u4efb\u536b\u751f\u90e8\u53e3\u8154\u79cd\u690d\u4e2d\u5fc3\u6280\u672f\u6307\u5bfc","post_extend6":"","post_extend7":"","post_extend8":""}";s:7:"isfixed";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_murl";s:0:"";s:10:"compatible";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"3";}i:3;a:32:{s:2:"id";s:2:"16";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:13:"post_keywords";s:0:"";s:6:"duties";s:12:"口腔医师";s:3:"job";s:12:"主治医生";s:12:"working_time";s:41:"11,21,31,41,51,61,71,13,23,33,43,53,63,73";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2000-01-01 00:00:00";s:7:"content";s:165:"<p>儿童及青少年早期预防性矫形治疗，成人固定矫正及无托槽隐形矫治技术，Tweed经典方丝弓矫治技术，肌功能矫形技术。</p>";s:4:"name";s:9:"杨冬梅";s:7:"term_id";s:1:"9";s:7:"excerpt";s:364:"<p>多年三甲医院口腔科工作经验，师从华西口腔副主任医生唐甜，培养出专业和精细的治疗技术，更是塑造出一位正畸医生的良好素质和认真负责工作作风，从初诊的耐心沟到方案的确定实施，期间碰到问题时的及时调整，再到最后的收尾和保持，耐心认真地做好每一步。</p>";s:11:"post_status";s:1:"1";s:14:"comment_status";s:1:"1";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-09-12 15:05:13";s:21:"post_content_filtered";N;s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";N;s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:5:"smeta";s:149:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258fce4eb19.jpg","thumb_phone":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258fd21cf8a.jpg","template":"","template_phone":""}";s:9:"post_hits";s:3:"567";s:9:"post_like";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:11:"recommended";s:1:"1";s:10:"post_phone";N;s:9:"link_type";s:1:"0";s:8:"post_url";s:0:"";s:11:"post_extend";s:611:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258fc1b5228.jpg","thumb1":"\/data\/upload\/20190709\/5d240c1aeb14b.jpg","post_extend1":"\u513f\u7ae5\u53ca\u9752\u5c11\u5e74\u65e9\u671f\u9884\u9632\u6027\u77eb\u5f62\u6cbb\u7597,\u6210\u4eba\u56fa\u5b9a\u77eb\u6b63\u53ca\u65e0\u6258\u69fd\u9690\u5f62\u77eb\u6cbb\u6280\u672f,\u808c\u529f\u80fd\u77eb\u5f62\u6280\u672f","post_extend2":"\u7259\u9f7f\u77eb\u6b63\u4e13\u79d1\u53f7","post_extend3":"5","post_extend4":"\u5373\u523b\u6b63\u63a8\u5e7f\u4e13\u5bb6","post_extend5":"\u5373\u523b\u6b63\u63a8\u5e7f\u4e13\u5bb6","post_extend6":"","post_extend7":"","post_extend8":""}";s:7:"isfixed";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_murl";s:0:"";s:10:"compatible";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"4";}i:4;a:32:{s:2:"id";s:2:"18";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:13:"post_keywords";s:0:"";s:6:"duties";s:12:"主治医师";s:3:"job";s:12:"主治医师";s:12:"working_time";s:41:"11,21,31,41,51,61,71,13,23,33,43,53,63,73";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2000-01-01 00:00:00";s:7:"content";s:79:"<p>传统固定矫正、隐形矫正技术及儿童错颌的早期干预。</p>";s:4:"name";s:9:"梅玉雯";s:7:"term_id";s:1:"9";s:7:"excerpt";s:400:"<p>毕业于南昌大学口腔医学专业，从事口腔临床工作近十年，多年</p><p>的公立医院口腔科工作经验，积累了大量丰富的口腔医疗经验，</p><p>掌握口腔医学国内外最新知识及正畸新技术的临床应用；</p><p>性格开朗，擅于和患者沟通，了解患者需求，用心对每位患者负责，深受广大患者信赖。</p><p><br/></p>";s:11:"post_status";s:1:"1";s:14:"comment_status";s:1:"1";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-11-06 17:57:44";s:21:"post_content_filtered";N;s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";N;s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:5:"smeta";s:149:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20181106\/5be165de4e574.jpg","thumb_phone":"\/data\/upload\/20181106\/5be165e233d61.png","template":"","template_phone":""}";s:9:"post_hits";s:3:"411";s:9:"post_like";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:11:"recommended";s:1:"1";s:10:"post_phone";N;s:9:"link_type";s:1:"0";s:8:"post_url";s:0:"";s:11:"post_extend";s:531:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20181106\/5be165d4c9bf9.png","thumb1":"\/data\/upload\/20190712\/5d2846481639a.jpg","post_extend1":"\u200b\u4f20\u7edf\u56fa\u5b9a\u77eb\u6b63\u3001\u9690\u5f62\u77eb\u6b63\u6280\u672f\u53ca\u513f\u7ae5\u9519\u988c\u7684\u65e9\u671f\u5e72\u9884\u3002","post_extend2":"\u7259\u9f7f\u77eb\u6b63\u4e13\u79d1\u53f7","post_extend3":"5","post_extend4":"\u5373\u523b\u6b63\u63a8\u5e7f\u4e13\u5bb6","post_extend5":"\u5373\u523b\u6b63\u63a8\u5e7f\u4e13\u5bb6","post_extend6":"","post_extend7":"","post_extend8":""}";s:7:"isfixed";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_murl";s:0:"";s:10:"compatible";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"5";}i:5;a:32:{s:2:"id";s:2:"14";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:13:"post_keywords";s:0:"";s:6:"duties";s:18:"牙齿修复主任";s:3:"job";s:12:"主治医师";s:12:"working_time";s:41:"11,21,31,41,51,61,71,13,23,33,43,53,63,73";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2000-01-01 00:00:00";s:7:"content";s:154:"<p>龋齿预防和树脂修补治疗、根管治疗、牙周病治疗、各种烤瓷冠、烤瓷桥修复、活动义齿的修复、常规牙拔除术</p>";s:4:"name";s:9:"王平昊";s:7:"term_id";s:2:"10";s:7:"excerpt";s:241:"<p>进修于西南医科大学，有丰富的口腔内科、口腔外科、口腔修复科的临床经验，擅长牙体牙髓疾病的治疗、牙周病治疗等。熟练掌握各类前牙后牙的根管治疗、拔除和修复技术。</p>";s:11:"post_status";s:1:"1";s:14:"comment_status";s:1:"1";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-08-22 15:43:25";s:21:"post_content_filtered";N;s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";N;s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:5:"smeta";s:149:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258fa6ca5a8.jpg","thumb_phone":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258faba982a.jpg","template":"","template_phone":""}";s:9:"post_hits";s:3:"503";s:9:"post_like";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:11:"recommended";s:1:"1";s:10:"post_phone";N;s:9:"link_type";s:1:"0";s:8:"post_url";s:0:"";s:11:"post_extend";s:675:"{"thumb":"\/data\/upload\/20190710\/5d258f979dc5f.jpg","thumb1":"\/data\/upload\/20190709\/5d240b8a33fde.jpg","post_extend1":"\u9f8b\u9f7f\u9884\u9632\u548c\u6811\u8102\u4fee\u8865\u6cbb\u7597\uff0c\u6839\u7ba1\u6cbb\u7597\u3001\u7259\u5468\u75c5\u6cbb\u7597\u3001\u5404\u79cd\u70e4\u74f7\u51a0\u3001\u70e4\u74f7\u6865\u4fee\u590d\u3001\u6d3b\u52a8\u4e49\u9f7f\u7684\u4fee\u590d\u3001\u5e38\u89c4\u7259\u62d4\u9664\u672f","post_extend2":"\u7259\u9f7f\u4fee\u590d\u4e13\u79d1\u53f7","post_extend3":"5","post_extend4":"\u5373\u523b\u7f8e\u63a8\u5e7f\u4e13\u5bb6","post_extend5":"\u5373\u523b\u7f8e\u63a8\u5e7f\u4e13\u5bb6","post_extend6":"","post_extend7":"","post_extend8":""}";s:7:"isfixed";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_murl";s:0:"";s:10:"compatible";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"9";}}